lines = Array[String](["[shake rate=5000 level=500 connected=0]-------------------------------------------[/shake]", "What the [shake rate=500 level=50 connected=0].-.-.-.-.[/shake] was that?", "Can you hea[shake rate=500 level=50 connected=0].-.[/shake] me?", "We’ve lost every link down here. How’s your connection?", "Hold on. I’m pulling your [color=#F20505]SatBoard[/color].", "...", "Oh [shake rate=500 level=50 connected=0].-.-.-.-.[/shake]", "That’s not good. ", "Listen.", "The [color=#F20505]Mother Soother[/color] system is offline and we don’t have time to reconnect it from base.", "Without it, the Mother’s event horizon starts expanding - and will swallow us whole.", "You have [color=#F20505]20 minutes[/color] to establish a link and restart the [color=#F20505]Soother[/color].", "You may need to route the signal through other satellites to reach long range.", "Find [color=#F20505]LRSAT-1[/color] on [color=#F20505]Aiga[/color]’s outer orbit."])

